Installation guide

On ubuntu 14.04

Install haskell plataform
Install wxHaskel which need wxWidget

To install wxwidget:
sudo apt-key adv --fetch-keys http://repos.codelite.org/CodeLite.asc

sudo apt-add-repository 'deb http://repos.codelite.org/wx3.0.1/ubuntu/ trusty universe'

sudo apt-get update

sudo apt-get install libwxbase3.0-0-unofficial libwxbase3.0-dev libwxgtk3.0-0-unofficial libwxgtk3.0-dev wx3.0-headers wx-common

To install wxHaskell:
cabal install wx

Install HNN

sudo apt-get install libgsl0-dev liblapack-dev libatlas-base-dev
cabal update
cabal install hmatrix

git clone git://github.com/alpmestan/HNN.git
cd HNN
cabal configure
cabal build
cabal install (to add it in your ghc package list, etc)
cabal haddock (to generate the documentation)
